<br>
First I have offered my services to you all through a officer to get you all into the rotation for VS who is needed for Wizard Epic parts. This Old Iky also drops the varrius peices of leg armor from Kunark. And a few Select peices of uber loots very nice items in other words. <br>
<br>
 To be able to be included in rotation you first must KS into said rotation. My sugestion to you is to go about it this way so that you can be included in the loot and fun. Alot of people have the attitude that they should be allowed to take a mob down anytime they chose and can levy the people to do so. I agree here but also see where the rotation opens up sportsmanship and good guild to guild relations in E-Marr. <br>
 I offer my services to OoT for my friends in your guild and well cause I think it is due time for the lower lvl guilds to be included in the loot. This mob is hard to do if done wrong but easy as hell if done right. Once you do it right and kill him you will say to yourselves why didn we do this before. I ask that you all give me your opinions on wether you want to be included in this and your opinions on the rotations. As it is now there are 11 guilds on the rotation and 3-5 Asian guilds KSing without intent on sticking to rotation. So yes it takes time to go all the way around the list but you are assured with a small exception the Kill when it is your turn. And the loot is well worth the wait. <br>
  You may all contact me in Game my characters names are-<br>
Tyvalius Valthalion 55 Magician <br>
Donjaun Juliani 28 Rogue <br>
 You may also reach me through Auviena Sreth and Dreadina.<br>
All three good friends and will vouch for my sincerity.<br>
<br>
Please Know this if you all decide as a guild to do this you must be there for each other when the time comes. All people are needed for this venture. Classes most depended on though are---- <br>
Enchanters With Rune 4 or 5<br>
Clerics lvl 53+ and all other clerics but try for 53 asap Divine Light is a must have for heals<br>
Druids Yes Druids are needed they make the difference in heasl when clerics cant do it all.<br>
Shaman SLOWs and Disease are a must with this necro.<br>
Tanks lvl 50+ with one needed to be lvl 57+<br>
<br>
Open up your guild bank and buy 100-200 peridots the sacrifice in pp is well worth the gains on dropping this fool.<br>
<br>
Please talk to me in game as alot is dependant on you decideing for yourselves you want to do this. <br>
Remember 90% of a successfull raid is dependant on people being there to support their guild.<br>
<br>
